/* Compatibility notes (compatReason) */
"你正在用 App Store 版微信，它被 macOS 沙盒限制、插件无法注入，所以多开用不了。\n\n需下载官网版 %@（约 470MB）并替换。安装时会关闭微信，聊天记录不会丢失。" = "You're using the App Store build of WeChat. It's restricted by the macOS sandbox, so the plugin can't be injected and multi-instance won't work.\n\nThe official build %@ (about 470 MB) needs to be downloaded and installed over it. WeChat will quit during installation; your chat history won't be lost.";
"当前微信 %@（%@）比插件支持的最新版（%@）还新，暂时用不了。\n\n需下载兼容版 %@（约 470MB）并替换。安装时会关闭微信，聊天记录不会丢失。" = "Your WeChat %1$@ (%2$@) is newer than the latest version the plugin supports (%3$@), so it won't work yet.\n\nThe compatible build %3$@ (about 470 MB) needs to be downloaded and installed over it. WeChat will quit during installation; your chat history won't be lost.";
"未检测到微信，需下载官网版 %@（约 470MB）安装。聊天记录（若有）不会丢失。" = "WeChat wasn't found. The official build %@ (about 470 MB) needs to be downloaded and installed. Your chat history (if any) won't be lost.";

